section.p:
3. Всеобщая форма стоимости.

\left.\begin{aligned}
\text{y товара}\ \mathbf{B}\\
\text{z товара}\ \mathbf{C}\\
\text{n товара}\ \mathbf{D}
\end{aligned}\right\}
=
\text{x товара}\ \mathbf{А}

section.code:
\left.\begin{aligned}
\text{y товара}\ \mathbf{B}\\
\text{z товара}\ \mathbf{C}\\
\text{n товара}\ \mathbf{D}\\
\text{и т. д.}
\end{aligned}\right\}
=
\text{x товара}\ \mathbf{А}
